Class VirtuosoBSCFilteredModel

java.lang.Object
  BSCcore.BSCModel
      BSCcore.VirtuosoBSCFilteredModel
All Implemented Interfaces:
Configurable, FilteredModel
public class VirtuosoBSCFilteredModel
extends BSCModel
implements FilteredModel, Configurable

VirtuosoBSCFilteredModel filters data from a Virtuoso Database for use within BiSciCol so we can reasonably traverse objects relating to a particular subject. This class uses SPARQL DESCRIBE queries to return BSCmodels. Sample usage: VirtuosoBSCFilteredModel q = new VirtuosoBSCFilteredModel( OntModelSpec.RDFS_MEM, "", null, QueryType.descendents); q.configure(sm); q.connect();
